</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Ethan Allens impulsive attack on Montreal on 25 Sept. ended in failure.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0175" class="document">Proceedings of the Committee of Conference, 1824 Oct. 1775</a>, Document II, Minutes of the Conference, n. 19.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0220-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>For Schuylers response, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0291" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 6 Nov. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
